'''大卫·斯塔尔·乔丹'''（David Starr Jordan，1851年1月19日-1931年9月19日），美國[[鱼类学|鱼类学家]]，曾任[[印第安纳大学布卢明顿分校|印第安纳大学布卢明顿分校]]校長以及[[斯坦福大学|斯坦福大学]]首任校长。他還是一位[[優生學|优生主义者]]，其发表過[[恐惧|恐惧]]种族退化的觀點；此外他还是一个反军国主义者，他起初反对美国参与[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=David Starr Jordan '72|url=http://ecommons.cornell.edu/bitstream/1813/25746/1/001_06.pdf|date=May 10, 1899|journal=Cornell Alumni News|issue=6|volume=I|pages=39, 43|access-date=2021-02-20|archive-date=2019-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212130959/https://ecommons.cornell.edu/bitstream/handle/1813/25746/001_06.pdf?sequence=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>David Starr Jordan ''The Blood of the Nation: A Study of the Decay of Races through the Survival of the Unfit.'' (copyright 1902, reprinted 1910) [https://play.google.com/books/reader?id=hfomB9SzXJQC&pg=GBS.PA12 p 12] {{Wayback|url=https://play.google.com/books/reader?id=hfomB9SzXJQC&pg=GBS.PA12|date=20201030191938}}. Note, the term 'race' occurs more than 30 times in this short book. The term 'eugenics' is not in there but the basic concept is described.</ref><ref name="Abrahamson1976">{{Cite journal|title=David Starr Jordan and American Antimilitarism|url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/40489774|last=Abrahamson|first=James L.|date=1976|journal=The Pacific Northwest Quarterly|issue=2|volume=67|pages=76–87|issn=0030-8803|jstor=40489774|access-date=2022-01-08|archive-date=2022-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220513051410/https://www.jstor.org/stable/40489774}}</ref>。

